CLINICAL-USE DISCLAIMER

MediGraph AI is provided for research, educational and demonstration purposes.
It is NOT a certified medical device and has not been cleared or approved by
the U.S. FDA, the India CDSCO, or any other regulator. Risk scores, care-gap
alerts and AI-generated answers are decision-support aids only and must not be
used as a substitute for the independent judgement of a qualified clinician.
All bundled data is synthetic and contains no real protected health information.
